WEBVTT

00:11.710 --> 00:18.380
[2010]

00:20.760 --> 00:21.440
Cold, huh?

00:33.560 --> 00:34.240
Cheng.

00:35.710 --> 00:37.390
Can you please not go?

00:39.790 --> 00:41.640
I can't always be by your side.

00:43.070 --> 00:44.470
You have to be a good girl.

00:45.310 --> 00:46.570
If anyone bullies you,

00:47.110 --> 00:48.370
just go to Jiang Cheng.

00:55.440 --> 00:56.390
You're a man now,

00:56.920 --> 00:58.850
so look after our sister properly.

01:00.520 --> 01:01.200
Cheng,

01:02.000 --> 01:03.000
come back soon.

01:16.340 --> 01:17.140
Be a good girl.

02:07.320 --> 02:08.000
Jin,

02:08.940 --> 02:10.919
just cry if you want to.

02:15.050 --> 02:15.920
I won't cry.

02:37.030 --> 02:37.710
I'm home.

02:51.800 --> 02:52.530
Jiang Cheng?

02:54.590 --> 02:55.320
Jiang Cheng!

03:09.430 --> 03:10.100
Zhou Jin.

03:13.120 --> 03:13.940
Hansheng.

04:46.409 --> 04:52.030
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:52.400 --> 04:54.730
[Episode 19]

05:25.220 --> 05:25.950
Officer,

05:26.430 --> 05:27.400
take my shoes off

05:27.740 --> 05:29.000
so I can loosen up a bit.

05:31.240 --> 05:33.170
I'm talking to you—did you hear me?

05:34.100 --> 05:35.659
Boss, Boss,

05:35.870 --> 05:37.020
well, something happened in his family.

05:37.020 --> 05:37.780
Just look at him.

05:37.780 --> 05:39.810
If there's anything you need, I'll do it!

05:39.810 --> 05:40.659
Get lost!

05:44.580 --> 05:45.780
Are you deaf today or what?

05:45.780 --> 05:47.380
Did your dad die, or your mom?

05:48.100 --> 05:48.960
Or did your girl

05:49.260 --> 05:50.790
get screwed by another guy?

05:53.830 --> 05:54.690
Say that again.

05:55.100 --> 05:56.040
I asked—

05:56.460 --> 05:57.550
did your dad die, or your mom?

05:57.550 --> 05:59.950
Or did your girl
get screwed by another guy?

06:08.220 --> 06:09.330
What happened after?

06:09.330 --> 06:11.240
It all died down after that.

06:11.900 --> 06:13.340
Criminals are human too.

06:13.360 --> 06:15.050
And humans fear death.

06:13.720 --> 06:15.110
[Dan]

06:17.830 --> 06:18.870
I'm going to take a call.

06:18.870 --> 06:19.260
Okay.

06:21.220 --> 06:22.630
Dan, what happened?

06:23.140 --> 06:24.740
Zhou Jin, come back quickly.

06:25.070 --> 06:25.950
What's wrong?

06:26.260 --> 06:27.510
Something's off with Jiang Cheng,

06:27.510 --> 06:28.700
and he won't say anything.

06:28.700 --> 06:30.030
You'd better come back.

06:31.430 --> 06:32.560
Does Chief Tan know?

06:33.220 --> 06:35.430
He's the one who asked me to call you.

06:35.850 --> 06:37.700
He wants you to question Jiang Cheng.

06:37.700 --> 06:39.750
He wouldn't say anything
about Old Scorpion

06:39.750 --> 06:41.700
or Leader Yao.

06:41.830 --> 06:43.830
He just kept asking if you were here.

06:43.830 --> 06:45.159
When will you come back?

06:46.950 --> 06:48.350
Okay, I'll be right back.

06:53.220 --> 06:53.630
Sirs.

06:55.580 --> 06:56.310
You're here.

07:00.390 --> 07:01.250
I remember you.

07:02.020 --> 07:03.280
On Zhao Xiaoyu's case.

07:03.950 --> 07:05.210
Hello, Commander Liu.

07:11.760 --> 07:14.090
Commander Liu, maybe just let her try?

07:14.870 --> 07:16.830
Investigations require efficiency.

07:16.830 --> 07:18.760
We can't let this standoff drag on.

07:22.900 --> 07:24.430
Let's see how it goes first.

07:27.580 --> 07:28.260
Zhou Jin!

07:29.310 --> 07:30.310
Zhou Jin!

07:30.330 --> 07:31.590
Stop yelling! Shut up!

07:32.950 --> 07:34.260
Alright, calm down.

07:34.580 --> 07:35.310
Jiang Cheng,

07:35.580 --> 07:37.430
what's in your best interest right now

07:37.430 --> 07:38.900
is to clearly explain what happened

07:38.900 --> 07:40.560
after the Jingang Wharf deal.

07:40.700 --> 07:42.460
Otherwise, the longer it drags on,

07:42.460 --> 07:44.120
the more suspicious we'll be.

07:45.220 --> 07:46.550
What do you mean by that?

07:48.630 --> 07:49.700
Haven't we always been

07:49.700 --> 07:50.960
talking to you nicely?

07:51.630 --> 07:52.990
Destroying the drug factory—

07:52.990 --> 07:54.720
yes, you do get credit for that.

07:55.310 --> 07:56.630
But please think about it:

07:56.630 --> 07:58.750
now the main culprits
are either dead or have fled.

07:58.750 --> 08:00.280
There's a lot we don't know,

08:00.340 --> 08:02.740
and you've never given us
a straight answer

08:03.310 --> 08:04.770
about how Leader Yao died.

08:05.450 --> 08:06.360
You said you're Cangfeng.

08:06.360 --> 08:07.750
Fine, we all believe you.

08:07.750 --> 08:09.750
But before everything
is investigated clearly,

08:09.750 --> 08:11.080
you're still suspected

08:11.140 --> 08:13.950
of involvement in
organized crime and intentional homicide.

08:13.950 --> 08:15.150
You can't avoid that.

08:15.900 --> 08:16.660
I told you,

08:16.900 --> 08:18.230
get Zhou Jin here for me.

08:26.870 --> 08:27.730
Commander Liu,

08:27.870 --> 08:29.390
although we can't fully prove

08:29.390 --> 08:30.950
that Jiang Cheng is innocent right now,

08:30.950 --> 08:32.880
if he really had something to hide,

08:33.070 --> 08:35.400
why would he have
passed information to us?

08:35.400 --> 08:36.340
Can I go in and talk

08:36.340 --> 08:36.909
to him?

08:37.990 --> 08:39.990
Why did he specifically ask for you?

08:42.679 --> 08:43.280
What

08:44.420 --> 08:46.150
exactly is your relationship?

08:48.160 --> 08:49.830
We were almost married.

08:55.080 --> 08:56.080
Professor Jiang.

09:00.790 --> 09:01.650
Commander Liu.

09:18.100 --> 09:18.960
Commander Liu,

09:19.030 --> 09:20.560
I wasn't finished just now.

09:21.200 --> 09:22.170
I promise

09:22.960 --> 09:24.110
I won't let my personal relationship

09:24.110 --> 09:26.070
with him affect my professional judgment.

09:26.070 --> 09:27.030
I know exactly

09:27.070 --> 09:28.160
what to ask

09:28.300 --> 09:29.900
and what to get him to answer.

09:30.050 --> 09:31.220
Right now, we're just stuck here.

09:31.220 --> 09:32.680
Why not let me go in and try?

09:32.770 --> 09:34.400
If it really doesn't work out,
I'll come back out.

09:34.400 --> 09:35.130
Is that okay?

09:35.190 --> 09:36.320
Yes, Commander Liu.

09:36.700 --> 09:37.970
Getting him to calm down

09:37.970 --> 09:38.690
and open up

09:38.850 --> 09:39.780
is the priority.

09:46.450 --> 09:47.650
Alright, I agree.

09:48.730 --> 09:49.480
Then...

09:49.760 --> 09:50.820
let's give it a try.

09:52.900 --> 09:53.760
Commander Liu,

09:54.460 --> 09:55.860
I'd like to speak with you

09:56.180 --> 09:57.110
about this case.

09:59.860 --> 10:00.460
Chief Tan.

10:01.920 --> 10:02.850
Let's pause for a moment.

10:02.850 --> 10:03.380
Yes.

10:15.730 --> 10:16.760
What's going on?

10:17.590 --> 10:18.800
What do you mean, what's going on?

10:18.800 --> 10:21.400
What's going on
between you and the guy inside?

10:22.030 --> 10:23.360
That was a long time ago.

10:25.350 --> 10:26.830
Then explain it clearly.

10:26.980 --> 10:29.840
What if your significant other
gets the wrong idea?

10:31.120 --> 10:33.050
I'll step out and take a look first.

11:18.310 --> 11:19.240
Why are you here?

11:20.240 --> 11:22.100
Just came to check on things here.

11:22.910 --> 11:24.640
What did you say to the leaders?

11:26.870 --> 11:27.400
Zhou Jin.

11:27.610 --> 11:28.110
Professor Jiang.

11:28.110 --> 11:29.110
Professor Jiang!

11:29.180 --> 11:30.230
The leaders have instructed us

11:30.230 --> 11:31.510
to fully cooperate with you

11:31.510 --> 11:33.110
and Professor Jiang's work.

11:33.930 --> 11:35.460
Although Jiang Cheng is
still under suspicion,

11:35.460 --> 11:37.630
questioning him in an interrogation room
isn't suitable.

11:37.630 --> 11:39.850
Undercovers have to maintain vigilance
for extended periods,

11:39.850 --> 11:42.610
making them highly sensitive
to changes in their environment.

11:42.610 --> 11:43.880
He must've been sleep-deprived
for a long time,

11:43.880 --> 11:45.520
which makes him sensitive to light.

11:45.520 --> 11:46.630
The lights in the interrogation room

11:46.630 --> 11:48.360
will only agitate him further.

11:48.990 --> 11:50.780
I've already suggested to the leaders

11:50.780 --> 11:51.250
that we move him

11:51.250 --> 11:53.110
to a less stressful environment.

11:53.350 --> 11:53.820
Also,

11:54.350 --> 11:56.480
turn off the surveillance equipment.

11:57.830 --> 11:58.280
Okay.

11:58.660 --> 11:59.990
Let us prepare for this.

12:00.150 --> 12:00.680
Let's go.

12:07.300 --> 12:07.870
Zhou Jin,

12:08.300 --> 12:09.700
you have only half an hour

12:09.790 --> 12:10.920
to question him.

12:26.060 --> 12:28.120
I know you've been worried about him.

12:28.780 --> 12:29.540
Don't rush.

12:30.870 --> 12:32.070
I'll be there for you.

13:07.110 --> 13:07.840
Jiang Cheng,

13:08.070 --> 13:09.600
we brought Zhou Jin for you.

13:09.960 --> 13:11.290
I hope you can stay calm.

13:23.440 --> 13:23.970
Alright.

13:26.270 --> 13:26.990
Jiang Cheng,

13:26.990 --> 13:29.450
everything you know
is very important to us.

13:30.040 --> 13:31.680
Laying out the situation clearly

13:31.680 --> 13:32.960
will help both you

13:33.300 --> 13:34.030
and the case.

13:47.870 --> 13:48.540
Jin.

13:58.400 --> 13:59.400
Jiang Hansheng.

13:59.770 --> 14:01.430
I mentioned him to you before.

14:02.750 --> 14:03.950
It's been a long time,

14:04.060 --> 14:04.880
Jiang Cheng.

14:08.620 --> 14:09.910
It's been a long time.

14:11.210 --> 14:12.250
You two have met?

14:12.280 --> 14:13.070
Of course.

14:13.400 --> 14:15.200
The young master from No. 23.

14:20.270 --> 14:21.150
Are you okay?

14:21.650 --> 14:23.270
Should we call a doctor to check on you?

14:23.270 --> 14:23.820
I'm fine.

14:35.910 --> 14:36.750
Jin,

14:37.820 --> 14:39.150
I've missed you so much.

14:42.810 --> 14:43.740
I need to ask you

14:44.470 --> 14:45.890
a few things.

14:50.420 --> 14:51.820
What do you want to ask me?

14:52.510 --> 14:54.040
Have I ever killed someone?

14:55.350 --> 14:56.270
I said I'm Cangfeng,

14:56.270 --> 14:58.060
and everything I've done
in the past five years

14:58.060 --> 14:59.110
was for the case,

14:59.700 --> 15:00.910
but did any of you believe me?

15:00.910 --> 15:01.940
I believe you.

15:04.460 --> 15:05.990
Jiang Cheng, I believe you.

15:07.350 --> 15:09.080
As long as you tell me the truth,

15:10.180 --> 15:11.080
I will help you.

15:15.660 --> 15:17.190
You've really changed a lot

15:17.910 --> 15:19.110
over the years.

15:24.270 --> 15:25.270
Sit down first.

15:26.970 --> 15:28.700
It wasn't easy to arrange this.

15:28.710 --> 15:30.270
You don't have much time left.

15:30.270 --> 15:31.930
You need to cooperate with me.

15:33.150 --> 15:33.630
Okay.

15:43.540 --> 15:44.470
Are you alright?

15:48.700 --> 15:50.390
Why did you insist on seeing Zhou Jin?

15:50.390 --> 15:51.450
Because I like her.

15:52.850 --> 15:54.010
Quit joking around.

15:54.250 --> 15:55.040
I'm not.

15:55.060 --> 15:56.520
Everything I said is true.

15:58.130 --> 15:59.730
Did Jin not tell you

16:00.330 --> 16:01.420
that we were together for seven years

16:01.420 --> 16:02.700
and even got engaged?

16:04.080 --> 16:05.270
The past is the past.

16:05.720 --> 16:06.650
You have a point.

16:07.320 --> 16:09.380
But some things can never be changed.

16:09.790 --> 16:12.090
Jin and I have had
so many misunderstandings.

16:12.090 --> 16:13.620
Now that we've finally met,

16:13.660 --> 16:14.390
there's so much

16:14.390 --> 16:16.350
I want to catch up on with her,
just the two of us.

16:16.350 --> 16:17.110
I think

16:17.830 --> 16:20.360
you can understand, right,
Professor Jiang?

16:21.730 --> 16:22.460
Jiang Cheng,

16:23.470 --> 16:25.380
this meeting today, in this environment,

16:25.380 --> 16:26.650
was arranged

16:26.890 --> 16:29.350
with my personal reputation
as a guarantee.

16:29.640 --> 16:30.470
We don't need

16:30.470 --> 16:32.730
to waste time on meaningless arguments.

16:33.860 --> 16:34.430
Also,

16:36.390 --> 16:38.120
it has already been turned off.

16:45.470 --> 16:46.930
I'll ask you one last time:

16:47.520 --> 16:49.580
why did you insist on seeing Zhou Jin?

16:53.370 --> 16:54.250
Who is the mole?

16:54.820 --> 16:56.550
He's the one who got Yao killed.

16:56.560 --> 16:57.130
Tell me!

17:02.420 --> 17:03.450
I can't tell you.

17:05.740 --> 17:07.339
Once we find out everything,

17:07.460 --> 17:09.260
he'll definitely pay the price.

17:09.950 --> 17:10.390
Tell me,

17:10.390 --> 17:12.050
how do you know there is a mole?

17:20.339 --> 17:21.339
How's your wound?

17:23.060 --> 17:23.740
I'm fine.

17:25.670 --> 17:27.670
When we were investigating Lai San,

17:27.670 --> 17:29.260
when Yao returned to your precinct,

17:29.260 --> 17:30.860
and even before you found me—

17:31.300 --> 17:34.580
this mole had been leaking the progress
of the police investigation.

17:34.580 --> 17:36.230
On the day of the Jingang Wharf deal,

17:36.230 --> 17:37.870
they took out Yao's photo

17:37.950 --> 17:39.580
and said he would definitely come.

17:39.580 --> 17:42.180
That's when I became
even more certain of this.

17:43.340 --> 17:44.530
After you escaped,

17:44.780 --> 17:46.110
what exactly did you do?

17:47.340 --> 17:49.060
How did Leader Yao

17:49.780 --> 17:50.980
and Meng Junfeng die?

17:54.190 --> 17:54.740
I...

18:01.740 --> 18:02.910
Under those circumstances,

18:02.910 --> 18:04.640
I really couldn't do anything.

18:05.780 --> 18:07.500
I could only watch as Old Scorpion

18:07.500 --> 18:08.580
killed them.

18:18.870 --> 18:19.470
Jin,

18:20.060 --> 18:21.020
there's something more important

18:21.020 --> 18:22.020
I need to tell you.

18:26.850 --> 18:27.230
For the past few years,

18:27.230 --> 18:29.100
I've been working for He Wu.

18:29.670 --> 18:30.990
You already know about his company,

18:30.990 --> 18:32.120
Hengyun Logistics.

18:32.260 --> 18:34.460
Besides transporting ordinary goods,

18:34.710 --> 18:37.110
they've also smuggled drugs and gun parts.

18:37.390 --> 18:39.250
I gave Yao a few USB drives before.

18:39.390 --> 18:40.260
Those drives contain

18:40.260 --> 18:41.500
videos of their deals

18:41.740 --> 18:44.150
and records
of their financial transactions.

18:44.150 --> 18:45.800
Yao kept all those USB drives

18:45.830 --> 18:47.540
in a safe-deposit box at Guangqi Bank.

18:47.540 --> 18:48.540
Whenever we got new evidence,

18:48.540 --> 18:49.670
he'd put it there.

18:50.060 --> 18:51.780
Originally, we planned to
settle everything

18:51.780 --> 18:53.300
once the operation concluded.

18:53.300 --> 18:54.430
Now that He Wu is dead

18:54.630 --> 18:55.500
and Old Scorpion has fled,

18:55.500 --> 18:56.830
many leads will go cold.

18:57.230 --> 18:58.710
As long as you retrieve those USB drives,

18:58.710 --> 19:01.640
you can thoroughly investigate
Hengyun Logistics.

19:01.920 --> 19:03.200
Now that my cover

19:03.230 --> 19:04.260
is blown,

19:04.260 --> 19:06.020
Old Scorpion will definitely make a move.

19:06.020 --> 19:07.260
So you must hurry.

19:10.540 --> 19:12.540
What kind of person is Old Scorpion?

19:16.260 --> 19:18.190
Old Scorpion is the sniper you saw.

19:23.260 --> 19:24.320
He is Old Scorpion?

19:26.860 --> 19:28.120
Qi Yan is Old Scorpion?

19:30.630 --> 19:31.830
I originally thought

19:32.610 --> 19:34.630
Qi Yan was Old Scorpion's subordinate too.

19:34.630 --> 19:35.670
It was only after coming to Jingang Wharf

19:35.670 --> 19:36.870
that I figured it out.

19:37.670 --> 19:39.200
I have to thank Yao for that.

19:39.670 --> 19:41.270
Because Yao recognized him.

19:41.540 --> 19:42.130
However,

19:42.150 --> 19:44.430
I've never heard anyone else
call him Qi Yan.

19:44.430 --> 19:45.670
Those close to him

19:45.740 --> 19:47.200
call him Young Master Wen.

19:47.500 --> 19:49.020
It seems like some kind of honorific

19:49.020 --> 19:50.060
or a nickname.

19:51.580 --> 19:53.150
This person usually
hides behind the scenes,

19:53.150 --> 19:54.430
lurking in the shadows.

19:54.430 --> 19:55.670
He has no public identity—

19:55.670 --> 19:56.670
none of us saw him in person

19:56.670 --> 19:58.730
unless it was absolutely necessary.

19:58.990 --> 19:59.950
He has an old man working under him

19:59.950 --> 20:01.260
who goes by the name Qi,

20:01.780 --> 20:03.640
whose words carry a lot of weight.

20:04.000 --> 20:04.910
For a long time, I'd believed

20:04.910 --> 20:06.060
Qi was Old Scorpion.

20:07.470 --> 20:08.990
He also has a woman under him

20:08.990 --> 20:09.870
named Qiu Ye.

20:10.060 --> 20:11.790
Qi Yan trusts those two deeply.

20:12.280 --> 20:13.190
After the Jingang Wharf deal,

20:13.190 --> 20:14.150
even though you sealed

20:14.150 --> 20:15.690
all the exits and mountain passes,

20:15.690 --> 20:16.550
it was useless.

20:17.260 --> 20:17.990
After abandoning

20:17.990 --> 20:19.250
their expendable men,

20:19.390 --> 20:21.470
their real bases are all underground.

20:21.470 --> 20:24.000
They split up
and moved to several locations.

20:24.100 --> 20:25.390
I was blindfolded the entire time,

20:25.390 --> 20:27.150
unable to tell day from night.

20:27.500 --> 20:29.230
I was just being dragged along.

20:29.630 --> 20:31.300
The Jingang Wharf deal was just a setup.

20:31.300 --> 20:32.710
It was designed to deal with Yao Weihai

20:32.710 --> 20:35.170
and the undercover
he'd planted in the gang.

20:36.500 --> 20:38.540
Old Scorpion no longer needs to
import drugs.

20:38.540 --> 20:40.910
He has mature manufacturing technology

20:41.060 --> 20:42.860
and a complete production line.

20:48.820 --> 20:51.080
Having investigated up to this point...

20:52.230 --> 20:53.760
you could've wrapped it up.

20:59.390 --> 21:00.230
But Yao died.

21:07.820 --> 21:09.780
Fortunately, you were smart enough

21:09.780 --> 21:10.720
to reach me.

21:11.820 --> 21:12.710
Even if I die,

21:12.710 --> 21:14.510
I have to pass on all the evidence

21:14.820 --> 21:15.430
and leads

21:15.430 --> 21:17.230
I've gathered over these years.

21:17.610 --> 21:19.410
Even if it only brings down He Wu,

21:20.260 --> 21:21.430
losing my life

21:22.260 --> 21:23.590
would still be worth it.

21:26.990 --> 21:28.230
They thought blindfolding me

21:28.230 --> 21:30.230
could hide the factory's location.

21:31.390 --> 21:32.540
But you know me.

21:33.230 --> 21:33.950
Remember the nickname

21:33.950 --> 21:35.550
you gave me when we were kids?

21:36.780 --> 21:37.580
Bloodhound.

21:38.340 --> 21:38.740
Yeah.

21:39.990 --> 21:41.650
My nose has always been sharp.

21:42.300 --> 21:44.430
Along the way,
I quietly kept track of the time

21:44.430 --> 21:46.630
and the directions the vehicle turned.

21:46.870 --> 21:48.160
Even if you hadn't come,

21:48.160 --> 21:51.360
I could've figured out
the exact location of the factory.

21:53.470 --> 21:55.160
That's all the intelligence

21:55.190 --> 21:56.520
I can provide right now.

21:57.340 --> 21:58.670
I have only one request—

21:59.260 --> 22:01.150
reinstate my identity
as a police officer ASAP.

22:01.150 --> 22:03.150
I want to catch Old Scorpion myself.

22:08.630 --> 22:09.150
Jin,

22:09.710 --> 22:10.580
believe me.

22:11.500 --> 22:12.430
I have never done anything

22:12.430 --> 22:13.760
that betrayed my faith.

22:14.740 --> 22:16.190
Five years is a long time.

22:16.780 --> 22:17.870
I can grit my teeth

22:17.900 --> 22:18.600
and bear everything

22:18.600 --> 22:20.340
that's happened.

22:20.360 --> 22:21.490
But from now on,

22:21.910 --> 22:24.970
I don't want my own people
talking behind my back again.

22:27.670 --> 22:28.530
I, Jiang Cheng,

22:29.470 --> 22:30.930
have a clear conscience.

22:36.630 --> 22:37.230
Jin.

22:38.740 --> 22:40.200
For the past five years...

22:42.540 --> 22:44.140
I was carrying out a mission.

22:44.780 --> 22:45.670
I had no choice.

22:59.360 --> 23:00.880
Right now, the most important thing

23:00.880 --> 23:02.280
is to find the USB drives.

23:02.590 --> 23:04.110
Once the evidence is secured,

23:04.110 --> 23:05.840
your identity will be obvious.

23:15.590 --> 23:16.220
Zhou Jin,

23:17.200 --> 23:18.460
go report to Chief Tan.

23:19.090 --> 23:20.490
The leaders are waiting.

23:26.060 --> 23:26.780
Trust me.

23:29.050 --> 23:31.110
I'll report everything truthfully.

23:57.500 --> 23:58.830
There will be news soon.

24:02.260 --> 24:03.260
It's about time.

24:05.540 --> 24:06.470
Jiang Hansheng.

24:07.950 --> 24:09.470
I remember warning you before

24:09.470 --> 24:11.470
to keep your distance from Zhou Jin.

24:11.990 --> 24:14.320
Now it seems you didn't take it seriously.

24:15.190 --> 24:16.520
We're already married.

24:22.670 --> 24:23.260
Unlike you,

24:23.260 --> 24:24.340
someone who was born

24:24.340 --> 24:25.470
with a silver spoon,

24:26.020 --> 24:27.620
I haven't had much in my life.

24:27.870 --> 24:29.990
But the things
that originally belonged to me,

24:29.990 --> 24:31.790
I don't intend to give up easily.

24:37.910 --> 24:39.310
Until you clear your name

24:39.580 --> 24:41.110
and restore your identity,

24:41.990 --> 24:43.520
stop asking to see Zhou Jin.

24:43.590 --> 24:44.420
Why?

24:44.820 --> 24:45.470
Remember,

24:46.630 --> 24:48.340
the only reason
you're still standing here today

24:48.340 --> 24:49.940
and able to see Zhou Jin at all

24:50.100 --> 24:51.150
is because of me.

24:55.060 --> 24:55.990
What did you say?

24:57.100 --> 24:58.950
Don't use your undercover work

24:59.790 --> 25:01.450
to guilt-trip Zhou Jin again.

25:11.790 --> 25:12.910
-Professor Jiang.
-Professor Jiang.

25:12.910 --> 25:13.470
Professor Jiang!

25:13.470 --> 25:14.470
Professor Jiang!

25:25.230 --> 25:26.490
Qi Yan is Old Scorpion.

25:26.710 --> 25:27.640
All the cases

25:27.670 --> 25:29.000
have traced back to him.

25:29.230 --> 25:30.390
With Jiang Cheng's statement

25:30.390 --> 25:31.390
combined with what I've learned

25:31.390 --> 25:32.580
at Guhua Prison,

25:32.710 --> 25:35.310
this line of clues
can basically be connected.

25:36.540 --> 25:37.150
Tell me.

25:37.990 --> 25:39.260
After the 8/17 Case,

25:39.580 --> 25:40.820
the police found evidence

25:40.820 --> 25:41.990
at the scene indicating the presence

25:41.990 --> 25:43.230
of two suspects.

25:43.870 --> 25:45.500
After the task force was established,

25:45.500 --> 25:46.230
Leader Yao—

25:46.650 --> 25:48.870
with the help of the Provincial Bureau's
Crime Research Lab—

25:48.870 --> 25:49.950
quickly located

25:50.150 --> 25:52.300
some suspects hiding in the suburbs.

25:52.710 --> 25:54.030
There were four of them.

25:54.030 --> 25:54.730
It was confirmed

25:54.730 --> 25:55.400
that Qi Yan

25:55.670 --> 25:56.930
was the prime culprit.

25:57.620 --> 25:58.680
But the other three

25:58.730 --> 26:00.490
didn't match the forensic profile

26:00.490 --> 26:02.020
of the second suspect.

26:02.770 --> 26:03.630
In other words,

26:03.930 --> 26:05.480
one of the killers
involved in my brother's murder

26:05.480 --> 26:06.690
escaped.

26:07.340 --> 26:09.170
And his gun was never found.

26:09.690 --> 26:11.250
So to find more clues,

26:11.730 --> 26:13.250
the task force investigated

26:13.250 --> 26:15.010
the network of the four who were shot.

26:15.010 --> 26:16.620
They got a lead through a man

26:16.650 --> 26:17.650
named Feng He.

26:17.930 --> 26:18.860
They discovered

26:18.970 --> 26:19.730
that Feng He

26:20.020 --> 26:22.140
had very close dealings with He Wen.

26:22.930 --> 26:23.890
So I believe

26:24.650 --> 26:26.310
that after tracing this lead,

26:27.330 --> 26:28.730
Leader Yao secretly launched

26:28.730 --> 26:31.380
the undercover operation
codenamed "Cangfeng."

26:31.380 --> 26:33.620
He sent Jiang Cheng to Guhua Prison

26:33.650 --> 26:34.780
to get close to He Wen

26:34.930 --> 26:36.100
and gain his trust.

26:36.490 --> 26:37.970
Therefore, after Jiang Cheng was released,

26:37.970 --> 26:40.020
he caught He Wu's eye

26:40.250 --> 26:41.170
and successfully infiltrated

26:41.170 --> 26:42.570
the criminal syndicate.

26:44.380 --> 26:45.440
What you've told me

26:46.170 --> 26:48.450
is completely consistent with
what Leader Yao

26:48.450 --> 26:49.250
briefed me on.

26:49.620 --> 26:50.300
And

26:50.820 --> 26:52.100
you've filled in

26:53.380 --> 26:55.110
many of the gaps he left behind.

26:56.060 --> 26:56.820
So,

26:57.490 --> 26:59.950
you're also willing to
believe Jiang Cheng?

27:00.490 --> 27:01.890
I believe he is Cangfeng—

27:02.300 --> 27:02.860
but

27:03.100 --> 27:04.300
not because I want to.

27:05.380 --> 27:06.490
It's because the files

27:06.490 --> 27:07.620
have now been

27:07.860 --> 27:10.120
declassified, clearly and completely.

27:17.900 --> 27:19.390
[Jiang Cheng] [Deputy Captain of
the Criminal Investigation Brigade 2,]

27:18.380 --> 27:20.300
The classification level for Cangfeng
was extremely high.

27:19.390 --> 27:20.890
[Fengzhou District,
Haizhou City, Binjiang Province]

27:20.690 --> 27:22.620
Unless they were killed, exposed,

27:22.620 --> 27:23.300
or

27:23.660 --> 27:25.190
[Codename: Cangfeng 1]

27:23.860 --> 27:25.190
returned successfully,

27:25.190 --> 27:27.590
[Person in charge: Yao Weihai,
Leader of the 8/17 Task Force]

27:25.380 --> 27:27.580
the files would never be declassified.

27:27.750 --> 27:30.510
[Conditions for Declassification:
Death, Total Exposure, or Successful Return]

27:27.890 --> 27:28.540
That's why

27:28.540 --> 27:30.540
we couldn't find the files earlier.

27:30.580 --> 27:32.020
It was the same for Meng Junfeng

27:32.020 --> 27:32.690
and

27:33.210 --> 27:34.140
for Jiang Cheng.

27:34.890 --> 27:36.950
Actually, both of them are Cangfeng—

27:38.170 --> 27:39.500
covering for each other

27:39.780 --> 27:41.110
and serving as backups.

27:41.140 --> 27:41.940
It was

27:42.820 --> 27:43.970
a double safeguard.

27:45.930 --> 27:47.060
If that's the case,

27:47.690 --> 27:49.080
does that mean Jiang Cheng's position

27:49.080 --> 27:50.620
as deputy captain will be restored soon?

27:50.620 --> 27:51.620
But don't forget—

27:52.860 --> 27:54.140
how do you explain

27:55.580 --> 27:57.180
the fingerprints on the gun?

28:00.820 --> 28:01.620
But earlier,

28:02.060 --> 28:04.140
after Jiang Cheng knew the camera was off,

28:04.140 --> 28:06.620
the first thing he asked me was
who the mole was.

28:06.620 --> 28:08.420
He was very agitated at the time.

28:08.740 --> 28:11.330
He said it was the mole
who got Leader Yao killed.

28:11.330 --> 28:12.290
I could see

28:13.140 --> 28:14.940
that his feelings for Leader Yao

28:15.100 --> 28:16.060
ran very deep.

28:47.210 --> 28:48.410
Finished reporting?

28:50.380 --> 28:51.910
It took more than two hours.

28:54.410 --> 28:56.070
Why haven't you gone back yet?

29:05.140 --> 29:05.870
Much better.

29:06.930 --> 29:08.460
Did you take your medicine?

29:08.930 --> 29:10.460
I'll take it when I get home.

29:11.580 --> 29:12.640
I'll take you back.

29:21.210 --> 29:21.820
Zhou Jin.

29:27.820 --> 29:28.880
Are you exhausted?

29:35.490 --> 29:36.210
No.

29:37.970 --> 29:39.030
I'm full of energy.

29:40.490 --> 29:41.100
Let's go.

30:19.490 --> 30:20.220
Come with me.

31:07.860 --> 31:08.590
Does it hurt?

31:14.580 --> 31:15.170
Yes.

31:17.610 --> 31:18.940
It's been a long time...

31:21.490 --> 31:23.020
since I felt this much pain.

31:31.820 --> 31:32.550
Hansheng...

31:37.420 --> 31:38.550
I'm so tired.

31:40.060 --> 31:40.730
I want...

31:43.580 --> 31:45.620
I want to find a place to hide.

31:51.990 --> 31:52.790
I understand.

31:55.170 --> 31:56.830
But none of this is your fault.

31:58.930 --> 32:00.340
It's all my fault.

32:04.930 --> 32:06.820
On August 17,

32:08.340 --> 32:10.940
my brother wasn't supposed to
take that shift.

32:12.820 --> 32:15.080
He switched with someone just so he could

32:16.300 --> 32:17.690
celebrate my birthday.

32:21.170 --> 32:23.570
When they notified us
to identify the body,

32:24.970 --> 32:27.630
I couldn't even bring myself to
go in and see him.

32:30.040 --> 32:30.850
I hid.

32:34.450 --> 32:37.100
But actually, my heart hurt so much.

32:39.730 --> 32:41.930
I was very depressed during those days.

32:43.540 --> 32:45.340
Jiang Cheng kept smoking

32:46.380 --> 32:47.340
one cigarette

32:48.300 --> 32:50.380
after another in front of me.

32:51.340 --> 32:53.540
We argued endlessly

32:54.380 --> 32:55.890
over the most trivial,

32:56.860 --> 32:58.490
petty things.

33:02.010 --> 33:02.970
I thought...

33:05.300 --> 33:07.250
my life would never be happy again.

33:09.970 --> 33:10.780
I changed.

33:12.300 --> 33:13.450
I stopped crying

33:14.890 --> 33:17.020
and stopped letting myself feel pain.

33:18.690 --> 33:20.480
I thought he'd changed too—

33:22.300 --> 33:23.900
that he had become a bastard.

33:28.580 --> 33:30.060
But I was wrong.

33:36.540 --> 33:37.860
He never changed.

33:48.930 --> 33:50.930
He's been lying to me for five years.

33:54.380 --> 33:56.860
And I actually believed it for five years.

34:00.820 --> 34:02.950
I actually believed it for five years.

34:10.780 --> 34:11.550
Hansheng.

34:14.170 --> 34:15.650
Did I fail him?

34:18.620 --> 34:19.989
Was I wrong?

34:22.730 --> 34:23.980
I feel so guilty.

34:27.170 --> 34:28.460
I feel like...

34:30.650 --> 34:32.370
I've failed everyone.

34:35.540 --> 34:36.810
I've failed...

34:43.370 --> 34:44.620
What should I do?

35:05.190 --> 35:05.840
Zhou Jin.

35:07.660 --> 35:08.490
You're tired.

35:11.180 --> 35:11.910
Sleep.

35:15.260 --> 35:16.320
I'll stay with you.

35:50.470 --> 35:51.050
Thank you, sir.

35:51.050 --> 35:51.650
Okay.

35:51.720 --> 35:52.630
You're welcome.

35:52.630 --> 35:53.630
Here, Jin.

35:54.030 --> 35:55.050
Thanks, Jiang Cheng.

35:55.050 --> 35:56.420
Where did you get the money for soda?

35:56.420 --> 35:57.340
Guess.

35:58.120 --> 36:00.120
How much allowance do you get a week?

36:01.700 --> 36:02.970
We're keeping secrets
from each other now, huh?

36:02.970 --> 36:05.170
Wait for me! Why are you walking so fast?

37:00.670 --> 37:01.270
Zhou Jin.

37:04.960 --> 37:05.960
What should I do?

37:32.370 --> 37:33.370
Professor Jiang.

37:34.170 --> 37:35.900
You're not asleep yet, are you?

37:36.610 --> 37:37.400
There's something

37:37.400 --> 37:39.000
I'd like to discuss with you.

37:50.290 --> 37:50.890
Chief Tan.

37:51.390 --> 37:51.990
Chief Tan.

37:52.890 --> 37:54.820
Jiang Cheng has disclosed that...

37:55.570 --> 37:56.600
evidence of Hengyun Logistics Company

37:56.600 --> 37:58.420
engaging in illegal transactions,

37:58.420 --> 38:00.890
along with the contact list
of He Wu's company,

38:00.890 --> 38:02.280
has been copied onto some USB drives.

38:02.280 --> 38:04.510
A USB drive is
currently in the Hongtian Building.

38:04.510 --> 38:05.640
Whether it's true or not,

38:05.640 --> 38:06.700
go and retrieve it.

38:07.620 --> 38:08.050
Yes.

38:10.250 --> 38:12.260
A USB drive is
in a locker on the 7th floor.

38:12.260 --> 38:13.320
When you get there,

38:13.410 --> 38:14.490
go to the front desk first

38:14.490 --> 38:15.820
and ask for the spare key.

38:15.820 --> 38:16.880
Don't get it wrong.

38:17.450 --> 38:18.980
Third column from the left,

38:19.100 --> 38:19.820
fifth row.

38:21.580 --> 38:23.000
It's best to go after work hours.

38:23.000 --> 38:23.860
Around 9:30 PM.

38:24.170 --> 38:25.230
Less crowded then.

39:07.690 --> 39:08.260
Freeze!

39:08.640 --> 39:09.660
Put the knife down.

39:09.660 --> 39:10.410
Hands up.

39:13.700 --> 39:15.530
-Freeze!
-Freeze!

39:17.130 --> 39:17.650
Freeze!

39:17.670 --> 39:18.330
Don't move!

39:19.510 --> 39:20.480
Don't come closer!

39:20.480 --> 39:21.730
You stay back too!

39:21.820 --> 39:22.570
Zhao Ping!

39:56.060 --> 39:56.780
Senior.

39:58.380 --> 39:59.150
You set me up.

40:08.600 --> 40:09.660
Why did you do this?

40:12.120 --> 40:13.720
You're not surprised at all.

40:14.370 --> 40:16.230
So you knew all along, didn't you?

40:16.700 --> 40:17.630
Come back with me

40:18.090 --> 40:19.250
and confess everything.

40:19.250 --> 40:20.310
Can I still go back,

40:21.230 --> 40:21.790
Senior?

40:21.840 --> 40:23.170
Don't call me "Senior"!

40:24.050 --> 40:27.010
Have you completely forgotten
the Police Academy's motto?

40:27.010 --> 40:28.740
The very first line is loyalty.

40:34.700 --> 40:35.620
I call you that

40:36.570 --> 40:38.920
because you said you like
"Armed Reaction."

40:38.920 --> 40:41.650
What does that have to do
with the Police Academy?

40:41.960 --> 40:42.560
Zhou Jin,

40:43.300 --> 40:44.630
I'm much older than you.

40:45.370 --> 40:47.900
I've let you ride
that privilege for too long.

40:48.290 --> 40:49.690
I'll say it one last time—

40:51.180 --> 40:52.180
come back with me.

40:52.210 --> 40:53.410
Don't pull that on me!

40:54.170 --> 40:55.980
Go ahead—give me three warnings,

40:55.980 --> 40:57.980
then shoot me for resisting arrest!

40:58.070 --> 40:58.670
Zhao Ping!

41:00.660 --> 41:01.790
Don't act like that!

41:02.740 --> 41:03.490
Come out.

41:04.260 --> 41:05.610
We'll talk when we get back.

41:05.610 --> 41:07.170
What are you guys doing?

41:07.940 --> 41:10.740
Stop looking at me
like you're heartbroken, okay?

41:10.990 --> 41:12.550
You are cops,

41:12.930 --> 41:14.370
and I'm a criminal!

41:15.170 --> 41:16.830
Why do you want to take me back?

41:17.300 --> 41:18.360
To interrogate me?

41:18.450 --> 41:20.580
To ask if I have some tragic backstory?

41:29.840 --> 41:31.160
Don't come closer!

41:37.840 --> 41:39.200
Why did you do this?

41:39.270 --> 41:40.230
For money!

41:45.780 --> 41:47.780
If I had gotten that USB drive today,

41:48.530 --> 41:49.780
one million would have been wired

41:49.780 --> 41:50.990
into my overseas account!

41:50.990 --> 41:52.650
How could I refuse that money?

41:53.090 --> 41:54.450
I'm not like you guys!

41:55.700 --> 41:57.360
All that so-called fairness,

41:57.890 --> 41:59.520
justice, and faith

41:59.860 --> 42:01.450
have nothing to do with me!

42:01.450 --> 42:02.420
You're not that kind of person!

42:02.420 --> 42:03.900
I am!

42:03.970 --> 42:05.330
This is the kind of person I am!

42:05.330 --> 42:06.390
I don't believe it!

42:07.270 --> 42:09.400
All these years,
you worked so hard on cases.

42:09.400 --> 42:10.860
Was all of that just an act?

42:15.050 --> 42:17.510
Zhou Jin, don't put
that kind of weight on me.

42:18.010 --> 42:20.470
I know you can't accept
what happened today.

42:20.800 --> 42:21.800
Idealism—

42:22.400 --> 42:23.730
who wouldn't want that?

42:24.130 --> 42:26.220
But fate isn't fair.

42:27.000 --> 42:29.610
It never laid out a straight road for me!

42:31.050 --> 42:33.580
You should understand that,
right, Zhou Jin?

42:34.370 --> 42:35.210
Sometimes,

42:35.780 --> 42:37.300
one bolt from the blue

42:38.700 --> 42:41.100
is enough to
change a person's entire life.

42:42.970 --> 42:43.900
Then tell me...

42:46.940 --> 42:48.220
what was

42:48.220 --> 42:49.680
that one bolt from the blue

42:50.180 --> 42:51.510
that changed your life?

42:56.860 --> 42:58.090
The same one as yours.

42:59.450 --> 43:00.250
The 8/17 Case.

43:02.260 --> 43:03.010
That day...

43:04.420 --> 43:05.090
I was there too.
